{"word":"βληχάομαι","slug":"βληχάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βληχάομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <a href='S:βληχή'><el>βληχή</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to bleat</i>, of sheep and goats, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; of infants, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}